text.author: Alyssa Marie
text.title: a day in the life vlog: spring cleaning + exploring black owned atlanta
text.summary: For spring cleaning, a vlogger goes over her old lipsticks in order to clear out expired ones, and decides to throw out her Too Faced Melted Matte Liquid, Ofra, Ashton Liquid and Urban Decay lipsticks, but not her favority red Pat McGrath lipstick, or the Dose of Color products which have no expiration date.
